<H3> <TI>   Cholera Vibrios Detected in Primorskiy Kray </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WE0016J Moscow PRAVDA in Russian 11 Sep 93 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 94WE0016J </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow PRAVDA </F>


