<F P=106> [Article by S. Kudryashov, journalist] </F>
  [Text] Ufa -- For the first time in many years, a severe 
toxic form of diptheria has been recorded in Ufa. A 21-year-old 
woman has died. Despite physicians efforts, the patient could 
not be saved. 
  In connection with the adverse diptheria epidemic situation, 
mass immunization of the adult population has begun in Ufa. 


