<F P=106> [Unattributed news agency brief] </F>
  [Text] Sochi -- Yet another person infected with the AIDS 
virus has been discovered in the city. He turned out to be a 
citizen of the United States working at one of Sochi's joint 
ventures. It is known that the American sought the services of 
