Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> [Reported by BETTA and Postfactum information agencies: </F>
``Under the Banner of Hepatitis Control''] 
  [Text]The residents of the Sakhalin village, Makarovo, will 
celebrate the First of May by fighting the hepatitis epidemic 
caused by decomposition of a cattle burying ground. As 
established by the staff of the rayon sanitary and 
epidemiological station, the hepatitis epidemic in this region 
has reached catastrophic proportions, and the number of cases 
has reached 82 cases to date. 


