<H3> <TI>   Diphtheria in Zhitomir </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WE0015A Kiev SILSKI VISTI in Ukrainian 1 Jul 93 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94WE0015A </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev SILSKI VISTI </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> [Article by S. Skorobogatko] </F>
  [Text] An extremely threatening situation with diphtheria 
has formed in the city of Zhitomir. Several cases of the illness 
have been recorded in the city. The City Executive Committee 
Commission on Emergency Situations has asked the population to 
urgently undergo prophylactic vaccination, and first of all to 
vaccinate the children. 

</TEXT>

