<F P=106> [From the Slakyanka Radio studio of the Russian Defense </F>
Ministry] 
  [Text] Minister of Foreign Economic Relations Oleg Davydov 
believes Russia has the potential to double its exports of 
military equipment in 1994. In 1993, Russia's arms exports 
